m heh. <br>  <br> The speed limit sign thing can go either way, but you were goin too fast to try and say you were speeding up because of the new speed zone, if you were at like 50 maybe, but not 60 heh. But he clocked you in a 35 zone, doesn't really matter if he pulled you over near a 45 sign <br> <p></p><span class="SignatureTitle">-----signature-----</span><div class="SignatureText">Biagio 50 Skald - Galahad <br> Ragnnd 50 Spirit Master - Kay <br> Ragnnd 50 Theurgist - Bors <br> Possobtwo 50 Bard - Lancelot <br>  <br> </div></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/post.asp?brd=20663&topic=70254026">Post Reply</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=70255855" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=537225">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=537225">Post History</a></td></tr><tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA"><td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%"><a href=" http://users.ign.com/about/Deamon_of_Darkness?boards=vn " class="AuthorLink">Deamon_of_Darkness</a>&nbsp;<a href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23stars"><img align=absmiddle src=http://media.ign.com/boardimages/star4.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="3,232 posts"></a><br><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><!-- WISH & COLL STUFF --><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr class="BoardRowA"><td nowrap="false" class="BoardRowA"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/collection/Deamon_of_Darkness"><font size="1">collection (0)</font></a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/wishlist/Deamon_of_Darkness"><font size="1">wishlist (0)</font></a></td></tr></table><!-- /WISH & COLL STUFF	--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Posts:</span> 3,232<br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Registered:</span> May 02<br></span><br></td><td class="BoardRowA" colspan=2 width="83%"><span style="font-we